// import_demo.rads - Demonstrates the basic import system
//
// To use this demo:
// 1. Create a file named "game_types.rads" with struct definitions
// 2. Import it using: import "game_types.rads";
// 3. Use the imported structs in your code
//
// Note: User-defined functions don't yet support parameters/returns,
// but structs work perfectly with imports!

// Example library file (game_types.rads):
/*
